name: Clan Raukaan
summary: Clan Raukaan, Clan Avernii, Clan Dorrvok, and Clan Garrsak of the Iron Hands Chapter assault an Eldar dig site on Dawnbreak. After destroying the Craftworld Alaitoc force protecting the site, they claim the relics for themselves and abandon the planet and its defenders, the 17th Catachan Army Group, to Eldar reprisals.
